OL,3,CWho was Donald Campbell, Bluebird's
OL,4,Cfamous pilot?
OL,6,FBluebird K7, the iconic water-speed
OL,7,Frecord breaking hydroplane, made its
OL,8,Freturn to Coniston over the weekend.
OL,10,FThousands of onlookers lined the
OL,11,Fstreets to see the boat driven to the
OL,12,Fvillage's Ruskin museum on the back of
OL,13,Fa truck.
OL,15,FAmong the crowd was Gina Campbell, the
OL,16,Fdaughter of Bluebird's famous pilot
OL,17,FDonald Campbell who died in 1967 in a
OL,18,Fhigh speed crash on Coniston Water.
