OL,3,CWho was Donald Campbell, Bluebird's
OL,4,Cfamous pilot?
OL,6,FBetween 1955 and 1964, the younger
OL,7,FCampbell set seven water-speed world
OL,8,Frecords in his Bluebird K7 craft. Four
OL,9,Fof these were on Coniston Water.
OL,11,FIn July 1964 he claimed the land speed
OL,12,Fprize at Lake Air salt flats in
OL,13,FAustralia, recording a speed of
OL,14,F403mph. He remains the only person to
OL,15,Fbreak the world land and water speed
OL,16,Frecords in the same year.
