OL,3,CWho was Donald Campbell, Bluebird's
OL,4,Cfamous pilot?
OL,6,FThree years later, he and Bluebird
OL,7,Fwere back on Coniston Water trying to
OL,8,Freach 300mph. Adverse weather caused
OL,9,Fsevere delays in the record attempt,
OL,10,Fcausing frustration in the team and in
OL,11,Fthe media.
