OL,3,CWho was Donald Campbell, Bluebird's
OL,4,Cfamous pilot?
OL,6,FCampbell eventually saw an opportunity
OL,7,Ffor the attempt on 4 January 1967.
OL,8,FTravelling at around 300mph, Bluebird
OL,9,Fleft the surface of the lake,
OL,10,Fsomersaulted and plunged nose-first
OL,11,Finto the water. Donald was killed
OL,12,Finstantly.JWhen K7 was recovered from
OL,13,Fthe lake in 2001, Donald Campbell's
OL,14,Fbody was also found. He was buried in
OL,15,FConiston where both he and his boat
OL,16,Fwill now remain.
